-- SNCB Holding May Pay to Use Freight Unit Assets, La Libre Says
-- B y   A o i f e   W h i t e
-- 2012-04-14T10:36:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-14/sncb-holding-may-pay-to-use-freight-unit-assets-la-libre-says.html
Belgium’s state-owned railroad
company  SNCB Holding (SNCVP)  may pay to use the assets of its freight
division, La Libre Belgique said, without citing any sources.  SNCB may pay tens of millions of euros to use SNCB
Logistics’ locomotives and a container hub at Antwerp port to
cover the unit’s deficit for around six months, the newspaper
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aoife White in Brussels at 
 awhite62@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anthony Aarons at   aaarons@bloomberg.net . 